WHAT IS IT?
-----------

  'HexiCon' is a Workbench game played on an hexagonally shaped
board, the idea is to rotate the links shown between the tiles so
they create an hexagon on the outermost tiles of the board.
Complete the game in the least amount of moves possible.

  Have fun!

FEATURES
--------

-Simple installation: just run the game and play!

-Small package, the 'LHA' archive is smaller than 50K, so it
 takes little time to download :)

-The game plays on the Workbench screen and its window is
 resizeable.

